    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-808b-9c28-e6cf9b5f2951",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "While ML to predict student performance is popular, there is a growing need to create models that are accurate but at a low-cost, something fuzzy-models can do. Then, it is important to choose optimal method and optimal parameters for a model. Authors explore the potential of AutoML to predict student performance. Multiple experiments seem to show approach is accurate.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-808b-9c28-e6cf9b5f2951",
        "parent": {
